NOT ONE OF THEM

92
00:06:21,032 --> 00:06:23,832
HAD A SINGLE STOLEN
WOOLONG ON THEM.

93
00:06:23,832 --> 00:06:27,365
WELL, THAT'S ALL
THE INFORMATION I COULD GET.

94
00:06:27,365 --> 00:06:28,332
HOW ABOUT YOU?

95
00:06:28,332 --> 00:06:30,165
