SUPPORT SOFTWARE.

105
00:06:50,899 --> 00:06:52,265
ACT NOW FOR THIS SPECIAL OFFER.

106
00:06:52,265 --> 00:06:55,899
FOR THE LOW INTRODUCTORY
PRICE OF 30,000 WOOLONGS,

107
00:06:55,899 --> 00:06:57,732
