137
00:08:13,299 --> 00:08:15,065
THEY'RE STILL OUR BEST CLUES.

138
00:08:15,065 --> 00:08:16,265
GIVE IT TO ED.

139
00:08:16,265 --> 00:08:17,199
HMM?

140
00:08:17,199 --> 00:08:18,332
