REALLY JUST A BIG GAME.

152
00:08:48,365 --> 00:08:52,032
GO AHEAD AND PLAY AGAINST
YOUR CYBER OPPONENT, ED.

153
00:08:52,032 --> 00:08:53,132
RIGHT.

154
00:08:53,132 --> 00:08:55,265
